item.title: Artificial Intelligence Meetup #1
item.description: Artificial Intelligence Group has grown up into something much bigger. From now on all the previous AI efforts will be combined under one new flag of “Artificial Intelligence Association of Lithuania”. Join our first official meetup to learn more about the organisation and how to become a part of it. Agenda Intro - Audrius Zujus (President @ Artificial Intelligence Association of Lithuania) “Deploy your neural net: engineering platform agnostic inference.
